A could feeling creeps down your spine as you watch the video footage found in the logfiles.
The three scientists were sitting at their workstations, not expecting a thing as the security door failed. Metrics indicated a rapid drop in temperature.
What followed was hard to put in words.
A strange entity entered the room, set off the emergency distress signal and disappeared.
Seconds later the scientists started to attack each other.
They seemed posessed by...something.
Whatever the strange entity planned by setting up this trap, nothing good could come from this.
It engineered to get you here, it surely wouldn't let you leave just like that.
You start running as fast as you can.
Mere feet away from your spaceship a massive energy barrier blocks the exit.
Can you circumvent it and return to safety? Be quick!
